Similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[627,798,1100,1125]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Wroughtonia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="41" pageNumber="442" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brachygena" status="sp. nov.">
