<figureCitation box="[1026,1110,1172,1197]" captionStart="FIGURE 11" captionStartId="25.[151,250,1460,1482]" captionTargetBox="[340,1247,339,1436]" captionTargetId="figure@25.[340,1247,339,1436]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="FIGURE 11. Wroughtonia brachygena sp. nov., â™€, holotype. A, wings; B, mesosoma, lateral aspect; C, propodeum, first and second metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect; D, hind femur and tibia, lateral aspect; E, propodeum, medio-dorsal aspect; F, habitus, lateral aspect; G, head, lateral aspect; H, head, dorsal aspect." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/827548/files/figure.png" pageId="41" pageNumber="442">Fig. 11</figureCitation>
